title: TJ Valašské Meziříčí
text: TJ Valašské Meziříčí (Tělovýchovná jednota Valašské Meziříčí) is a polisports club and <a href="association%20football">football</a> club located in <a href="Vala%C5%A1sk%C3%A9%20Mezi%C5%99%C3%AD%C4%8D%C3%AD">Valašské Meziříčí</a>, <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>. It currently plays in <a href="Moravian%E2%80%93Silesian%20Football%20League">MSFL</a>, which is the third tier of the <a href="Czech%20Republic%20football%20league%20system">Czech football system</a>.
